{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "1b87ea86-4ba4-4541-b1c0-eac95a53dbf5", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1b87ea86-4ba4-4541-b1c0-eac95a53dbf5@2.pkg/1772602042236/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602042867", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1b87ea86-4ba4-4541-b1c0-eac95a53dbf5@2.pkg/1772602042236/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602042867"}, "identifier": "1b87ea86-4ba4-4541-b1c0-eac95a53dbf5", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>解答此题的关键是在理解诗句内容的基础上来划分即可。划分诗歌的节奏第一步是划出句中的主谓部分，第二步是把有多个定语的划分出来。D错误；正确的朗读节奏应为&ldquo;为什么/我的眼里/常含泪水？/因为/我对这土地/爱得深沉&rdquo;</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列诗句的朗读节奏划分错误的一项是（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列诗句的朗读节奏划分错误的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1b87ea86-4ba4-4541-b1c0-eac95a53dbf5@2.pkg/item.json?v=1752736774713", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_id